- Typography guidelines
- Visual hierarchy for role display

@CTW: Please prepare documentation templates for this feature.

🟢 **Copy/Technical Writer (CTW)**: I'll create these documentation items:
- API documentation for the RoleManager
- User guide for role switching
- Developer guide for extending roles

